{"tid":783272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"反黑警員疑跌市輸股票 彩園邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-08-17T11:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T14:58:05.000Z","uid":112702,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a2d2d633d0c228c40ee70e9a33fd71d5dfdff2","tid":783272,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"消息指，死者為大埔反黑組探員<br />\n<br />\n上水彩園邨彩湖樓，凌晨2時42分，30歲姓陳警員被發現從高層走廊墮下，倒臥地下昏迷，保安員發現報警。救護員到場送院，搶救終於不治。據稱，事主受金錢問題困擾，警方撿獲遺書，調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓陳，30歲，消息指他為大埔反黑組探員，最近曾向同僚透露在股票市場投資失利，於跌市中輸錢，鬱鬱不歡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d056253494a30a0bb7ae2a7a8ea00fa306717507","tid":783272,"uid":76855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"點解啲人可以玩到跳樓"},{"pid":"8d8386f3fd0e5e6ab70c0990a18e4344d9ca3b99","tid":783272,"uid":119769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ec865627177dafb797b85c0d3c72bef47bae8a0","tid":783272,"uid":4787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d8386f3fd0e5e6ab70c0990a18e4344d9ca3b99","tid":783272,"uid":119769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"見到佢地我都想講rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19efe3f358ee057b6c518b8b8f9801db4df0857c","tid":783272,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e21c9009d6d7a3099cd9fcd939e0d3dd1797df6","tid":783272,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"又烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/